er, Dust with the Green Sponge Crumbs, on top and Cut 100 grams each per portion and serve chilled", "ingredients": "Water, Colours (Sunset Yellow E110 , Brilliant Blue E133), Acidity Regulator (Citric Acid E330), Preservative (Sodium Benzoate E211)"}}, {"id": 8800, "name": "Cup Cake Women Day", "kcal": 382.0, "contains": ["Gluten", "Eggs", "Milk"], "may_contain": [], "source": "recipes", "details": {"method": "Prepare the Vanilla Muffin Batter and add the strawberry Compote, Unifilar the Batter into 50 Grams each Before Baking.Bake at 160 Deg C, cool it Down, Pipe Pink Color Butter Cream 20 Grams Each Serve Chilled.", "ingredients": "Disodium Diphosphate (E450i), Sodium Hydrogen Carbonate (E500ii), Wheat Flour"}}, {"id": 8801, "name": "Cumin Powder", "kcal": 420.0, "contains": [], "may_contain": [], "source": "recipes", "details": {}}, {"id": 8802, "name": "Stromboli /Calzone  Dough G& G", "kcal": 266.0, "contains": ["Gluten", "Eggs", "Milk"], "may_contain": ["Mustard", "Soya"], "source": "recipes", "details": {"method": "Prepare the stromboli dough by adding all the ingredients in mixing bowl or dough kneebar, expect the salt and oil.slow speed for 4 mins and high speed for 12 mins, once the dough becomes smooth and elastic add the salt and oil continue kneading for 3 mins till the oil been absorbed by dough.Once the dough is ready, rest in chiller and use as required."}}, {"id": 8803, "name": "Raspberry Jelly  G&G", "kcal": 161.0, "contains": [], "may_contain": [], "source": "recipes", "details": {"method": "In a clean Saucepan, Boil the frozen raspberry with water add Sugar and Agar for 2 mins, remove from the heat and cool it down, use as required."}}, {"id": 8804, "name": "Raspberry Cheese Cake G&G", "kcal": 272.0, "contains": ["Gluten", "Milk", "Soya", "Sulphites"], "may_contain": [], "source": "recipes", "details": {"method": "Powder the biscuits, add soft butter, brown sugar, and honey, Pour 20 Grams Biscuit Base in Transparent Glass.Pour Vanilla Cheese Mou